snippet: Heat center Hassan Whiteside let his frustrations show after Miami's double-overtime loss to Orlando on Tuesday night, complaining about his lack of touches in the final minutes....
lead_paragraph: Heat center Hassan Whiteside let his frustrations show after Miami's double-overtime loss to Orlando on Tuesday night, complaining about his lack of touches in the final minutes.
